data.description:
Discover the perfect blend of country living and modern comfort on this 5-acre equestrian estate. This charming property, built in 1991, is a haven for horse enthusiasts and has much to offer. Barn: Well-equipped with three stalls, a tack room, a wash bay, an arena, an outside shelter, a hay loft, and a lush pasture. Living Spaces: Enjoy a spacious eat-in kitchen with an island and sliding glass doors leading to the back patio. The massive family room is filled with ample windows, a gas fireplace, and provides access to the deck. Additional Ground Floor Spaces: You'll find a welcoming foyer, a large office with French doors, a laundry room, and a convenient half bath. Bedrooms: Three generously sized bedrooms, all with plentiful closets. One bedroom includes an en suite bathroom, and there are two more full bathrooms. Basement: It's clean and partially finished with some built-in workshop cabinetry. Outdoor Amenities: A wrap-around back deck connected to an above-ground pool, a four-car garage, wood fencing, a patio, an outbuilding, and a shed on this 5-acre property.
Make this unique property your home and retreat. Call or text today for your Private Showing!
